Alternatively, may be {{Han compound|魚|羊|t1=fish|t2=sheep|ls=ic|nocap=y}} – delicious.

===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*sar||new; fresh}}. Cognate with {{cog|tbq-pro|*g-sar||new; fresh}}, whence {{cog|bo|གསར་བ||new; fresh}}, {{cog|raw|angsar||new}}, {{cog|duu|aksal||new}}, {{cog|lus|tʰarᴴ||new}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}); cognate with {{cog|bo|གསར་||new}}, {{cog|my|ဆန်း||new, fresh}} ({{zh-ref|Hill, 2019}}).

